      • NoteModificationResult

        public NoteModificationResult()
        Creates an empty result object

      • NoteModificationResult

        public NoteModificationResult(NoteModificationStatus status,
                              Collection<String> unresolvableBlogs,
                              Collection<String> unwritableBlogs,
                              Long noteId,
                              Long version,
                              boolean direct,
                              UserNotificationResult userNotificationResult)
        Creates an result object.
        Parameters:
        status - the status of the creation / modification
        unresolvableBlogs - collection of blog aliases that could not be resolved to existing blogs
        unwritableBlogs - collection of cross post target blog aliases the user has no write access to.
        noteId - ID of the created note
        version - the version of the note
        direct - true if the note is a direct message
        userNotificationResult - the notification result
